posts.text: The update to my Twitter/X course is live! https://dagorenouf.com/how-to-dominate-twitter/…

The story of a startup in 10 memes.

1. We're all naive at the beginning
We stopped chasing money a while ago.
I'm currently on stage 2 of the startup founder's journey

My wife and I decided to give up on our startup 
@logologydesign
 

It was a tough decision to make, especially after spending 5 years and almost all of our savings to bootstrap it.

But the reality is that despite our best efforts, we never found a way to grow beyond survival
